com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom

Enum DOMNodePosition

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DOMNodePosition>
      • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom.DOMNodePosition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable< DOMNodePosition> 

    public enum DOMNodePosition
extends java.lang.Enum<DOMNodePosition>
    This enumeration represents position of the DOMNode against another DOMNode in the same or different documents.
    此枚举表示DOMNode在相同或不同文档中相对于另一个DOMNode的位置。
    See Also:
    DOM API specification
